# API keys & tokens
- Never embed long-lived Google API keys in client code.
- Provide a tiny `/server` function to mint **short-lived** tokens or relay the WS.
- Scrub PII from logs; mask keys in devtools.

# Cursor indexing
- Add `.cursorignore` to exclude `.env*`, `/server/.env*`, and any capture artifacts.
